<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        
body {
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
}

header {
    color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

header .logo h1 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
}

nav ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

nav ul li {
    display: inline;
    margin-right: 20px;
}

nav ul li a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.2em;
}

nav ul li a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

.about-us {
    padding: 50px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #fff;
    color: #333;
}

.about-us h2 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.about-us p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
}

.about-us h3 {
    font-size: 2em;
    margin-top: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.about-us ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    font-size: 1.2em;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.about-us ul li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
}

footer .footer-content p {
    font-size: 1em;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <h1><strong>SAHAL STORE</strong></h1>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="about-us">
        <div style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;" class="content">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>At FoodDelivery, we're passionate about bringing you the best meals right to your doorstep. Whether you're craving a quick snack, a hearty lunch, or a fancy dinner, we ensure that every dish is delivered with care and speed. Our team works tirelessly to ensure a seamless experience for our customers.</p>
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>We strive to make food delivery easier, faster, and more enjoyable for everyone. Our goal is to bring high-quality food from your favorite restaurants straight to your door, while making sure the experience is convenient and delightful.</p>
            <h3>Our Values</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Quality: Only the best ingredients for every meal.</li>
                <li>Convenience: Fast and reliable delivery, every time.</li>
                <li>Customer First: Always striving to provide the best experience.</li>
                <li>Variety: A diverse selection of meals to suit every taste.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; 2025 FoodDelivery. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
